Package com.sportradar.livedata.sdk.common.networking

Interface GatewayListener

public interface GatewayListener
Represents a listener used to observe Gateway implementation.
Author:
uros.bregar

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void onConnected()
    Invoked by the observed Gateway instance when it establishes a connection to the server.
    void onDataReceived​(InputStream stream)
    Invoked by the observed Gateway instance when it receives new data from the server.
    void onDisconnected​(Exception ex)
    Invoked by the observed Gateway instance when it's connection to the server is dropped.

  • Method Details

    • onDataReceived

      void onDataReceived​(InputStream stream)
      Invoked by the observed Gateway instance when it receives new data from the server.
      Parameters:
      stream - The InputStream containing the received data.

    • onConnected

      void onConnected()
      Invoked by the observed Gateway instance when it establishes a connection to the server.

    • onDisconnected

      void onDisconnected​(Exception ex)
      Invoked by the observed Gateway instance when it's connection to the server is dropped.
      Parameters:
      ex - The Exception which caused the connection to be dropped, or a null reference if disconnect operation was requested.
